{"sections":{"main":{"type":"main-page","disabled":true,"settings":{"padding_top":28,"padding_bottom":28}},"rich_text_hFzJbK":{"type":"rich-text","blocks":{"heading_TRKaQJ":{"type":"heading","settings":{"heading":"About Us","heading_size":"h1"}},"text_zXgLD9":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<p>私たちについて<\/p>"}}},"block_order":["heading_TRKaQJ","text_zXgLD9"],"settings":{"desktop_content_position":"center","content_alignment":"center","color_scheme":"","full_width":true,"padding_top":0,"padding_bottom":0}},"rich_text_w9CmYA":{"type":"rich-text","blocks":{"heading_ePPpjt":{"type":"heading","settings":{"heading":"“Re:Jewelry”で、日常に輝きを。","heading_size":"h1"}},"text_kYQEhF":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<p>mj bijou（エムジェイ ビジュー）は、運営元MIX JEMの頭文字「mj」と、フランス語で「ジュエリー」を意味する「bijou」を組み合わせた名前です。<br\/>18年以上の経験を活かし、確かな目利きで厳選したジュエリーをお届けします。<\/p>"}},"text_EtVM8X":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<p>ジュエリーは、時を経ても価値を持ち続けるもの。<br\/>mj bijouは、適切なケアによって2次流通品の本来の輝きを引き出し、ジュエリーの美しさを再発見できる機会を提供します。<br\/>身につけるたびに愛着が増し、日常が華やぐ――そんなジュエリーとの出会いをお届けすることが、私たちの使命です。<\/p>"}}},"block_order":["heading_ePPpjt","text_kYQEhF","text_EtVM8X"],"custom_css":["h2.rich-text__heading {color: #292929; font-size: 2.4rem; font-weight: 700; font-family: \"Noto Sans JP\", sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.1em; margin-bottom: 3.4rem;}","@media screen and (max-width: 767px) {h2.rich-text__heading {font-size: 1.8rem; }}",".rich-text__text {color: #292929; text-align: left; line-height: 2; margin-bottom: 2.4rem; letter-spacing: 0.1em; max-width: 72rem; width: 100%; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;}"],"settings":{"desktop_content_position":"center","content_alignment":"center","color_scheme":"","full_width":true,"padding_top":0,"padding_bottom":0}},"rich_text_kiJ8L8":{"type":"rich-text","blocks":{"heading_eKW3FT":{"type":"heading","settings":{"heading":"mj bijou<span>3<\/span>つのこだわり","heading_size":"h1"}}},"block_order":["heading_eKW3FT"],"custom_css":[".rich-text {margin-top: 11.4rem; margin-bottom: -1.8rem;}","h2.ric